{"tid":720661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北辰促抽樣鑿沙中線紅磡站混凝土驗鋼筋","createTime":"2018-06-28T05:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T05:50:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18816a1e0201d95b7daad60b618af9bac8910dda","tid":720661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1016290&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1016290%26csid%3D261_341&d=biwqld0qdl1yqvFOcMZWBb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b5251680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1016290&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n田北辰促抽樣鑿沙中線紅磡站混凝土驗鋼筋<br />\n28.06.2018 12:58<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n田北辰促抽樣鑿開紅磡站工程混凝土檢驗(商台新聞 陳業輝攝)<br />\n<br />\n立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席田北辰指，港鐵沙中線紅磡站擴建工程分判商中科興業、董事總經理潘焯鴻已表明親眼目睹月台層有鋼筋被剪短，而且數目遠超港鐵所指的數量，田北辰認為目前已有合理理據抽樣鑿開混凝土檢驗，他對運輸及房屋局長陳帆昨日表示，要有更多科學理據才決定是否鑿開混凝土，表示非常失望。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員涂謹申呼籲警方盡快和潘焯鴻聯絡，盡快索取相關的手機，還原有人剪短鋼筋的片段，否則警方將遺失很重要的證據。"},{"pid":"6bd3e982b3efeb1255e71d49ddf60c6b4718fd84","tid":720661,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"5000 仲抽乜<br />\n拆左佢起過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffae9fd9d3a14c8b56934d2c5356f7f26c37342b","tid":720661,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"UGL 五千萬 五千支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}